---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Blog"
description: "Guides and setup advice for building a golf simulator that fits your space."
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100/70 px-8 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 md:text-5xl">Sim build guides</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600">Evidence-based guidance on sizing a room, selecting gear, and avoiding costly mismatches.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-16">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:shadow-md">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-400">
        <span>{{ post.date | date("%Y") }}</span>
        <span>-</span>
        <span>FitMySim</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
        <a class="transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:text-slate-700" href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
      <a class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:text-emerald-800" href="{{ post.url }}">
        Read the guide ->
      </a>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>